reviews.reviewText: I absolutely love this charger. It’s so light weight and it charges it super fast. The best part is the two cords and two bases. And I love that when it’s charging you have the light that comes on so you aren’t guessing if it’s charging or not.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great cords a little wobbly adapter
reviews.reviewText: There’s typically either one way to go or the other with this type of product, either it’s good quality or it’s just not. This one so far seems pretty solid quality. The cords are really nice, and a whole lot better than the others I’ve gotten with sets similar to this one. The usb slots are pretty firm which is important for me as I’m not gentle all the time when I forget I’m plugged in and try to run off without unplugging my phone. The outlet does come out of the port fairly easily but it isn’t super loose. The blue light on it is pretty bright. Overall I’d definitely recommend it and if I need another I’d order it again. I didn’t pay attention and thought it would be two USBc to usbc cords but it’s fine as one of my iPhones still uses lightning so I still get use out of the lightning cord.
